    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "It appears that this only happens while tasks are running in the threadpool (ie getting sticker packs). If cmd+q is pressed while stickers are being fetched, the app will not fully quit until that thread has completed its tasks.\r\n\r\nLikely the tasks being run in the threadpool will need some kind of a short circuit ability.",
